com.misc.common.moplaf.time.continuous

Interface CapacityChange

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, EventsProvider, EventsProviderAbstract, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, com.misc.common.moplaf.propagator.ObjectWithPropagatorFunctionAdapter
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CapacityChangeImpl

    public interface CapacityChange
extends EventsProvider
    A representation of the model object 'Capacity Change'. A change in Amount for an given interval of time. The value of the Distribution is increased by the given Amount at the start of the interval of time and decreased by the same Amount at the end of the interval of time.

    The following features are supported:

    • Start
    • End
    • Amount
    • Start Event
    • End Event
    See Also:
    ContinuousPackage.getCapacityChange()
